        </linklist>
        <comment>LAT1 is activated by Syk, 
Phosphorylated LAT 1 recruits PLCγ, SLP-76,SOS and adapter proteins, such as Gads, Grb2, and Shc.
(Alvarez-Errico et al., 2009)
