          <link xlink:href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=12743571"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>Fc epsilon RI induction of ERK, JNK and p38 MAP kinase cascades results in the activation of transcription factors regulating the AP-1 complex ( c-jun, ATF-2 ) and NF-AT, NF-kB, which are crucial for immune response signaling.
(Lorentz et al., 2003)</comment>
      </annotation>
