          <link xlink:href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=20610546"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>Fc epsilon RI induction of ERK, JNK and p38 MAP kinase cascades result in the activation of transcription factors regulating the AP-1 complex ( c-jun, ATF-2 ) and NF-AT, NF-kB, which are crucial for immune response signaling. 
(Kim et al., 2011; Iwaki et al., 2005; Balagopalan et al., 2010)</comment>
