      <comment>This regulatory graph and the associated logical rules account for current data on mast cell activation in wild type and mutant conditions.
This logical model has been established on the basis of a detailed molecular map,  which can be found in the Reactome database (cf. enclosed link), along with further annotations.
The model and its analysis have been thoroughly presented in Niarakis et al  (2014).
</comment>
